## Release v9.3.0

## Balancing

- Increased drone life to make them more viable
- Decreased drop chance of the shot speed buff
- Capped player shot speed at 2.5 (without the buff drop)
- Decreased the selling price multiplier based on the current level for goods

### Misc

- Simplified buff sytem code
- Slightly changed NPC dialog
- Improved manual

## Files included

- `void-merchants.p8` — PICO-8 standard cart in clear text format
- `void-merchants.p8.png` — PICO-8 cart image
- `void-merchants_linux.zip` — Linux binaries
- `void-merchants_windows.zip` — Windows binaries
- `void-merchants_raspi.zip` — Raspberry Pi binaries
- `void-merchants_osx.zip` — macOS binaries
- `manual.txt` — Manual for this release
- `LICENSE.txt` — Licensing information